13:55.900 --> 13:57.561
WHAT'S YOUR PROBLEM?

13:57.570 --> 13:59.094
NOTHING --

13:59.100 --> 14:02.035
JUST THAT I'M OFFICIALLY FAILING
MECHANICAL ENGINEERING,

14:02.040 --> 14:03.405
WHICH WOULDN'T BE A PROBLEM

14:03.410 --> 14:05.401
EXCEPT I WANT TO BE
A MECHANICAL ENGINEER.

14:05.410 --> 14:08.004
I'VE ALWAYS WANTED TO BE
A MECHANICAL ENGINEER,

14:08.010 --> 14:09.807
AND I'VE NEVER FAILED
ANYTHING.

14:09.810 --> 14:11.778
YOU NEED TO CHILL.

14:11.780 --> 14:12.974
I DO?

14:12.980 --> 14:14.277
THAN KS.

14:14.280 --> 14:15.577
GOOD TO KNOW.

14:15.580 --> 14:18.185
WASN'T IT EN VOGUE WHO TAUGHT US
ALL TO FREE OUR MINDS,

14:18.190 --> 14:19.817
AS THE REST WOULD FOLLOW?

14:19.820 --> 14:21.412
AND THAT MEANS WHAT?

14:21.420 --> 14:25.356
IT MEANS
WE'RE GOING OUT TONIGHT.

14:28.100 --> 14:29.795
MR. O'DELL, IT'S KEITH MARS.

14:29.800 --> 14:31.062
I'VE GOT GOOD NEWS.

14:31.070 --> 14:32.594
I'VE LOCATED
YOUR WIFE'S EX-HUSBAND,

14:32.600 --> 14:35.763
AND HE'S RIGHT HERE
IN SUNNY SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA.

14:35.770 --> 14:36.907
HOW'D YOU FIND HIM?

14:36.910 --> 14:38.138
HE LEFT A TRAIL
OF EX-WIVES.

14:38.140 --> 14:39.664
IT LED YOU STRAIGHT
TO THE CORNER

14:39.670 --> 14:41.729
WHERE HE WAS PASSING OUT FLYERS
DRESSED AS A CELLPHONE?

14:41.740 --> 14:45.005
THE MANAGER OF HIS RATHOLE
APARTMENT LET ME IN HIS PLACE --

14:45.010 --> 14:46.568
ONE BEDROOM,

14:46.580 --> 14:49.344
LOTS OF BACK STAGE WESTS WITH
AUDITIONS CIRCLED.

14:49.350 --> 14:51.386
APPARENTLY HE'S SCRATCHING OUT
A LIVING

14:51.390 --> 14:53.187
WORKING AS
A VOICE-OVER ACTOR.

14:53.190 --> 14:55.385
I THINK I'VE GOT A PLAN
TO ARRANGE A MEETING

14:55.390 --> 14:58.257
BETWEEN YOU, YOUR WIFE,
AND MR. BATANDO.

15:06.970 --> 15:09.438
[ DOG BARKING ]

15:20.980 --> 15:23.119
HOPE YOU DON'T MIND.

15:23.120 --> 15:25.111
ONE OF THE COCKROACHES
LET ME IN.

15:25.120 --> 15:27.611
SO, WHERE'D YOU STASH
MY NECKLACE?

15:34.230 --> 15:38.792
YOU CAN LET HIM GO. BACKUP
AND ME -- WE'RE OLD FRIENDS.

15:38.800 --> 15:40.438
WHERE'S LILLY'S NECKLACE?

15:40.440 --> 15:43.898
SOMEONE LEFT A BRACELET
IN MY BED LAST WEEK.

15:43.910 --> 15:46.265
OH, WAIT,
WAS IT A HOOP EARRING?

15:46.270 --> 15:47.828
I'M NOT PLAYING WITH YOU.

15:47.840 --> 15:50.343
DON'T YOU GET IT? I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

15:50.350 --> 15:52.648
OH, YOU DON'T, HUH?
LET ME SPELL IT OUT.

15:52.650 --> 15:55.312
I TELL YOU ABOUT
A WORKING ON-CAMPUS CASINO.

15:55.320 --> 15:58.539
SIX HOURS LATER, IT'S HELD UP BY
A GUY YOUR SIZE WEARING A MASK,

15:58.550 --> 16:01.610
WHO HAPPENS TO BE COVERED
IN A THIN FILM OF DRYWALL DUST

16:01.620 --> 16:03.986
AND THE STENCH
OF DRAKKAR COLOGNE.

16:03.990 --> 16:06.356
MY COLOGNE STINKS?

16:06.360 --> 16:10.160
SO, ALL THIS PLAY I'VE BEEN
GETTING IS FROM PURE SEX APPEAL?

16:10.170 --> 16:11.489
YOU JUST TOLD MY CLASSMATES

16:11.500 --> 16:13.695
THAT YOUR OLD LIFE OF CRIME
WAS CALLING.

16:13.700 --> 16:16.362
YOU JUST ASKED ME
ABOUT LILLY'S NECKLACE.

16:16.370 --> 16:19.362
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU THINK
I'D DO THAT...TO YOU...

16:19.370 --> 16:21.372
AFTER ALL
WE'VE BEEN THROUGH.

16:21.380 --> 16:24.406
AFTER ALL WE'VE BEEN THROUGH,
CAN YOU REALLY BLAME ME?

16:28.320 --> 16:30.185
HEY, BACKUP, YOU CAN STAY.

16:30.190 --> 16:32.146
YOUR GIRL'S GOT TO GO.

16:32.150 --> 16:33.583
[ SCOFFS ]

16:37.190 --> 16:40.125
IT'S A WONDER
YOU DON'T HAVE MORE FRIENDS.

16:44.030 --> 16:45.099
I'M HERE.

16:45.100 --> 16:46.260
WHEW!

16:46.270 --> 16:47.931
SORRY I'M LATE.
HI, CLIFF.

16:47.940 --> 16:49.134
YOU REMEMBER THE JOB?

16:49.140 --> 16:51.335
PRETEND TO BE
YOUR RECEPTIONIST.

16:51.340 --> 16:55.003
I JUST WISH I HAD SOME
LIFE EXPERIENCE TO DRAW FROM.

16:55.010 --> 16:56.204
CLIFFORD, YOU READY?

16:56.210 --> 16:57.802
RACE FANS, HOT-RODDERS,

16:57.810 --> 17:01.268
THE MONSTER TRUCKS ARE COMING
TO NEPTUNE, NEPTUNE, NEPTUNE!

17:01.280 --> 17:03.180
THAT'S GREAT, CLIFF,
BUT JUST REMEMBER --

17:03.190 --> 17:05.784
SUNDAY! SUNDAY! SUNDAY!

17:06.990 --> 17:08.548
[ CHUCKLES ]

17:14.630 --> 17:16.393
Cliff:
CERTAIN RESTRICTIONS MAY APPLY.

17:16.400 --> 17:17.628
"NO VIDEO, FLASH PHOTOGRAPHY,

17:17.630 --> 17:19.268
"OR OTHER
RECORDING DEVICES ALLOWED

17:20.770 --> 17:22.499
"OF THE MONSTER TRUCK
ASSOCIATION OF AMERICA.

17:22.500 --> 17:24.263
PLEASE DRINK RESPONSIBLY."

17:24.270 --> 17:26.135
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

17:26.140 --> 17:29.303
HI, I'M HERE
FOR THE AUDITION.

17:29.310 --> 17:30.504
STEVE BATAN DO.

17:30.510 --> 17:32.068
GREAT.
I'LL TAKE YOUR RSUM.

17:32.080 --> 17:33.479
SIGN IN.
THEY'LL BE RIGHT WITH YOU.

17:33.480 --> 17:36.119
SO, MICKEY,
YOU BOOK THAT OLIVE GARDEN GIG?

17:36.120 --> 17:38.145
WAITING TO HEAR.

17:41.290 --> 17:42.552
Veronica: YEAH.

17:42.560 --> 17:45.654
MICKEY,
THEY'RE READY FOR YOU.

17:45.660 --> 17:48.857
SOMEONE WANT TO TAKE MY TURN?
I'M STILL DIALING IT IN.

17:48.860 --> 17:50.020
GO AHEAD IF YOU WANT.

17:50.030 --> 17:51.463
YOU SURE?

17:51.470 --> 17:53.335
GREAT.

17:53.340 --> 17:55.535
OVER THERE?
Veronica: MM-HMM.

18:02.140 --> 18:03.744
STEVE.

18:03.750 --> 18:05.502
WELCOME.

18:06.950 --> 18:07.939
WHAT THE...

18:08.580 --> 18:11.140
NO, NO, NO,
WE'RE NOT DOING THIS.

18:11.150 --> 18:12.981
YOU CAN LEAVE IN A MINUTE.

18:12.990 --> 18:14.412
FIRST YOU'RE GONNA LISTEN.

18:14.420 --> 18:16.786
MINDY, WHAT THE HELL
IS THIS ABOUT -- ALIMONY?

18:16.790 --> 18:19.281
I MEAN,
IS THIS WHAT YOU'VE STOOPED TO?

18:19.290 --> 18:20.996
THIS ISN'T ABOUT MONEY,
STEVE.

18:21.000 --> 18:24.219
I JUST NEEDED TO TALK TO YOU,
AND I DIDN'T KNOW ANY OTHER WAY.

18:24.230 --> 18:25.663
NO OTHER WAY?

18:29.270 --> 18:31.238
JASON IS DYING.

18:31.240 --> 18:33.606
HE HAS BONE CANCER,

18:33.610 --> 18:37.171
AND HE NEEDS
A BONE-MARROW TRANSPLANT.

18:39.080 --> 18:41.071
HE NEEDS YOU, STEVE.

18:41.080 --> 18:42.445
HOW DO YOU KNOW
I'M A MATCH?

18:42.450 --> 18:43.610
FROM THE PATERNITY TEST.

18:43.620 --> 18:46.418
YOU ARE A MATCH,
THANK GOD.

18:46.420 --> 18:48.308
HE NEEDS YOU, STEVE.

18:48.320 --> 18:50.322
CAN YOU DO THIS?

18:50.330 --> 18:52.184
THIS IS YOUR CHANCE,
STEVE.

18:52.190 --> 18:53.896
YOU CAN BE HIS DAD AGAIN.

18:53.900 --> 18:56.789
DO THIS.

18:56.800 --> 18:57.721
PLEASE.

18:57.730 --> 18:59.027
YOU KNOW SOMETHING?

18:59.030 --> 19:02.534
THERE WAS A TIME
WHEN I COULD HAVE BEEN AROUND.

19:02.540 --> 19:04.633
I COULD HAVE BEEN THERE
FOR JASON,

19:04.640 --> 19:07.336
BUT YOU KEPT ME AWAY
FROM HIM.

19:07.340 --> 19:09.069
YOU TURNED HIM AGAINST ME.

19:09.080 --> 19:10.570
I DID NO SUCH THING.

19:10.580 --> 19:12.445
YOU LEFT ME BECAUSE
I WASN'T MAKING ENOUGH MONEY.

19:12.450 --> 19:14.441
I LEFT YOU
BECAUSE YOU WERE LAZY,

19:14.450 --> 19:16.748
'CAUSE YOU WANTED EVERYTHING
TO COME EASY.

19:16.750 --> 19:19.480
CAREFUL. DON'T FORGET,
YOU'RE ASKING ME A FAVOR.

19:19.490 --> 19:20.582
A FAVOR?

19:20.590 --> 19:22.581
YES, PLEASE, STEVE,
DO US A FAVOR

19:22.590 --> 19:25.388
AND SEE IF YOU CAN ACT LIKE AN
ACTUAL HUMAN FOR THREE SECONDS

19:25.390 --> 19:27.494
OUT OF YOUR OTHERWISE
COMPLETELY WORTHLESS LIFE.

19:27.500 --> 19:29.297
YOU'RE GOING TO DO THIS.

19:29.300 --> 19:30.722
I DON'T CARE IF I HAVE TO
BREAK YOU IN HALF

19:30.730 --> 19:32.391
AND SUCK THE MARROW
OUT OF YOUR BONES MYSELF.

19:32.400 --> 19:34.288
YOU'RE GOING TO DO THIS
FOR YOUR SON.

19:34.300 --> 19:35.892
HE'S NOT MY SON.

19:35.900 --> 19:37.037
HE'S YOUR SON.

19:37.710 --> 19:41.032
SHE MADE THAT
PERFECT LY CLEAR.

19:41.040 --> 19:43.804
[ Crying ] NO.

20:06.900 --> 20:08.367
HEY!

20:08.370 --> 20:09.894
IT'S JOE COLLEGE!

20:09.900 --> 20:11.458
JOS LUNCHPAIL --

20:11.470 --> 20:13.973
THE LIVING, BREATHING EMBODIMENT
OF THE AMERICAN DREAM.

20:15.540 --> 20:16.871
PUNCH ANY CLOCKS LATELY?

20:16.880 --> 20:19.348
ARE YOU LINING UP
YOUR NEXT GIRLFRIEND?

20:19.350 --> 20:20.840
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]

20:23.650 --> 20:27.711
I'M GUESSING
THIS LOWRIDER'S YOURS?

20:30.290 --> 20:31.928
ANY REASON
WHY EVERYONE SUSPECT S ME

20:31.930 --> 20:34.854
FOR A CRIME I DON'T EVEN KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT?

20:34.860 --> 20:37.328
GOT 'EM.

20:37.330 --> 20:41.938
THEY MATCH
THE ROBBERY DESCRIPTION.

20:41.940 --> 20:43.362
YIKES.

20:43.370 --> 20:45.964
HEY, WHAT DO YOU SAY
WE DO YOUR MIRANDA RIGHTS

20:45.970 --> 20:47.232
IN HARMONY THIS TIME?

20:47.240 --> 20:48.468
I'LL TAKE LEAD.

20:48.480 --> 20:50.004
YOU TAKE TENOR?

20:50.010 --> 20:52.501
IS IT DJ VU WHEN SOMETHING
HAPPENS MORE THAN TWICE,

20:52.510 --> 20:54.410
OR IS THAT
SOMETHING DIFFERENT?

20:54.420 --> 20:56.342
I'LL HAVE TO
LOOK THAT UP.

21:02.390 --> 21:05.188
ASK FOR CELL "B."
IT HAS THE BEST LIGHT.

21:05.190 --> 21:06.748
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

21:11.700 --> 21:16.262
HEY, GOOD-LOOKING, WE'LL BE BACK
TO PICK YOU UP LATER.

21:28.550 --> 21:30.074
SACKS TELLS ME
YOU'RE HERE TO SEE WEEVIL.

21:30.080 --> 21:32.810
PLANNING ON HELPING HIM
BEAT ANOTHER RAP?

21:32.820 --> 21:35.209
ACTUALLY, I'M HERE
TO GET MY NECKLACE BACK.

21:35.220 --> 21:36.812
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

21:36.820 --> 21:40.358
YOU ACTUALLY BELIEVE
THAT THE BAD GUY DID IT?

21:43.930 --> 21:45.488
[ Imitating robot ]
DOES NOT COMPUTE.

21:45.500 --> 21:48.560
DOES NOT COMPUTE.

21:48.570 --> 21:50.663
YOU MUST HAVE BEEN FUN
IN THE '805.

21:50.670 --> 21:53.377
SO, YOU GET A TIP ABOUT
THE WATCHES IN WEEVIL'S CAR?

21:53.380 --> 21:54.369
BETTER.

21:54.380 --> 21:55.836
HE USED A STOLEN CREDIT CARD

21:55.840 --> 21:57.899
FROM ONE OF THE WALLETS LIFTED
IN THE CASINO HOLDUP.

21:57.910 --> 22:00.970
CHARGED A PIZZA
FROM MAMA MIA PIZZA.

22:00.980 --> 22:05.588
CRIMINAL MASTERMIND HAD IT
DELIVERED TO HIS OWN APARTMENT.

22:09.660 --> 22:12.424
BE IT EVER SO HUMBLE.

22:12.430 --> 22:13.692
Weevil: YEAH.

22:13.700 --> 22:16.294
I'M THINKING
OF SOME CURTAINS OVER HERE,

22:16.300 --> 22:18.621
MAYBE A KOI POND
IN THE CORNER.

22:18.630 --> 22:19.995
WHERE'S MY NECKLACE?

22:20.000 --> 22:21.069
I DON'T HAVE IT.

22:21.070 --> 22:23.197
IT WAS A FRAME JOB, "V."

22:23.200 --> 22:26.966
LOOK, A PREPAID PIZZA
WAS DELIVERED TO MY APARTMENT.

22:26.970 --> 22:28.335
I DIDN'T ORDER IT.

22:28.340 --> 22:31.309
COME ON, WHAT'S A WORKING MAN
GONNA DO IN THAT SITUATION?

22:31.310 --> 22:34.074
SO, WHEN I LOOK INTO THIS --
AND I WILL LOOK INTO THIS --

22:34.080 --> 22:36.640
I'M GONNA FIND OUT
YOU DIDN'T ORDER THAT PIZZA?

22:36.650 --> 22:39.289
OR YOU COULD JUST
SAVE YOURSELF THE TROUBLE

22:39.290 --> 22:40.917
AND TAKE MY WORD FOR IT.

22:41.990 --> 22:44.424
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

22:44.430 --> 22:45.886
OKAY.

22:45.890 --> 22:46.879
THAT WAS GOOD.

22:46.890 --> 22:48.357
WELL DONE.

22:53.900 --> 22:55.936
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

22:57.610 --> 22:59.931
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

23:03.750 --> 23:06.105
SURPRISE.
SURPRISE. URSPRISE.

23:06.110 --> 23:07.975
REDENBACHER
AND "THE HILLS HAVE EYES."

23:07.980 --> 23:10.540
YOU REMEMBER CHLOE AND JESSICA
FROM LAST NIGHT.

23:10.550 --> 23:11.744
INSTANT PARTY.

23:11.750 --> 23:13.240
YOU GUYS, I'M STUDYING.

23:13.250 --> 23:16.014
STUDY LATER.
LET'S HAVE FUN.
YEAH, WALLACE.

23:16.020 --> 23:16.987
I CAN'T, Y'ALL.

23:16.990 --> 23:18.582
I THOUGHT
YOU MIGHT SAY THAT,

23:18.590 --> 23:20.421
AND THAT'S WHY
I BROUGHT YOU THIS.

23:20.430 --> 23:21.920
CALL THIS NUMBER.

23:21.930 --> 23:22.919
IT'S A TUTOR.

23:22.930 --> 23:24.591
IS HE GOOD?
MIRACLE WORKER.

23:24.600 --> 23:27.068
GOT ME THROUGH A COURSE
LAST YEAR -- AND A HARD ONE.

23:27.070 --> 23:28.298
YOU'RE A P.E. MAJOR.

23:28.300 --> 23:29.289
PLEASE.

23:29.300 --> 23:30.631
KIN ESIOLOGY.

23:31.810 --> 23:35.632
FEELING BETTER ALREADY,
AREN'T YOU?

23:37.580 --> 23:39.707
Danny:
TAKE THE COMPLEX MAP.

23:42.720 --> 23:45.484
HI,
I'M LOOKING FOR THE MANAGER.

23:45.490 --> 23:46.741
HE OR SHE AROUND?

23:46.750 --> 23:48.786
YOU'RE VERONICA MARS.

23:48.790 --> 23:52.521
AND YOU'RE...DANNY.

23:52.530 --> 23:53.599
ROSSOW.

23:53.600 --> 23:54.828
YEAH, I AM.

23:54.830 --> 23:56.923
COOL.

23:56.930 --> 24:00.422
YOU WENT TO MY SCHOOL LAST YEAR.
I GO TO NEPTUNE HIGH.

24:00.430 --> 24:02.159
LUCKY YOU.

24:02.170 --> 24:04.263
YOU REMEMBER WHEN THOSE BIKERS
TAPED THAT GUY TO THE FLAGPOLE

24:04.270 --> 24:06.431
AND YOU JUST WALKED UP THERE
AND CU-IYl'E-IAIH' DOWN?

24:06.440 --> 24:09.773
REMEMBER WHEN YOU
STOPPED THOSE GUYS FROM
BLOWING UP THE SCHOOL?

24:09.780 --> 24:11.975
NO ONE WAS GONNA
BLOW UP THE SCHOOL.

24:11.980 --> 24:15.347
SO, WHAT I WAS GOING TO --
ON THE LAST DAY, I REALLY
WANTED YOU TO SIGN MY YEARBOOK.

24:15.350 --> 24:18.080
DANNY,
I'M WORKING ON A CASE NOW.

24:18.090 --> 24:20.513
THAT IS SO AWESOME.

24:20.520 --> 24:21.817
YEAH, IT IS.

24:21.820 --> 24:24.084
IT'S SO AWESOME,
AND I NEED YOUR HELP.

24:24.090 --> 24:27.719
AN ORDER WENT OUT LAST NIGHT
TO 1172 NAVASOTA.

24:27.730 --> 24:29.891
DO YOU GUYS
HAVE CALLER I.D.?

24:29.900 --> 24:31.663
WELL,
WE'RE TOTALLY COMPUTERIZED.

24:31.670 --> 24:32.819
THE ORDER COMES IN.

24:32.830 --> 24:34.229
IT LOGS THE PHONE NUMBER.

24:34.240 --> 24:35.992
THAT WAY,
WE CAN ANSWER THE PHONE LIKE,

24:36.000 --> 24:37.604
"MR. SMITH,
THANKS FOR CALLING AGAIN.

24:37.610 --> 24:39.965
ANOTHER PEPPERONI LOVERS
FOR YOU AND THE MISSUS."

24:39.970 --> 24:41.733
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:41.740 --> 24:44.208
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

24:50.720 --> 24:53.416
1172 NAVASOTA?

24:53.420 --> 24:54.910
[ SIGHS ]

24:54.920 --> 24:57.286
IT WASN'T A CALL-IN.
IT WAS AN INTERNET ORDER.

24:57.290 --> 24:58.757
REALLY?

24:58.760 --> 25:00.955
ANY WAY OF KNOWING
WHERE THE ORDER CAME IN FROM?

25:00.960 --> 25:02.848
ONLY OUR MANAGER,
MR. WOLFCASTLE,

25:02.860 --> 25:05.499
CAN MAKE THOSE REQUESTS FROM
OUR INTERNET SERVICE PROVIDER,

25:05.500 --> 25:07.161
AND HE'S NOT HERE.

25:08.140 --> 25:10.529
ANY WAY WE CAN
MAKE LIKE HE IS?

25:15.340 --> 25:18.571
[ German accent ] HELLO,
THIS IS WALTER WOLFCASTLE.

25:18.580 --> 25:20.969
WITH WHO AM I SPEAKING?

25:20.980 --> 25:24.143
LISTEN, I NEED A FAVOR
'CAUSE MY HANDS ARE FULL.

25:24.150 --> 25:29.213
I NEED YOU TO TRACK
AN INTERNET ORDER.

25:29.220 --> 25:30.756
OF COURSE I WANT IT NOW.

25:30.760 --> 25:33.524
WHAT?
SHOULD I WAIT TILL TUESDAY?

25:36.160 --> 25:39.163
THANKS TO MY ONE-MAN FAN CLUB,
I NOW KNOW

25:39.170 --> 25:42.594
PRECISELY WHICH COMPUTER THE
PIZZA ORDER WAS PLACED FROM --

25:42.600 --> 25:44.409
A PUBLIC HEARST COLLEGE
COMPUTER HUB

25:44.410 --> 25:48.506
JUST 40 FEET AWAY FROM
WHERE WEEVIL WAS DRYWALLING,

25:48.510 --> 25:49.909
SO HE STAYS IN THE MIX.

25:49.910 --> 25:52.071
THEN AGAIN,
SO DO HUNDREDS OF PEOPLE

25:52.080 --> 25:54.640
WHO PASS THROUGH HERE
EVERY DAY.

25:54.650 --> 25:55.969
HELLO, SQUARE ONE.

25:55.980 --> 25:59.040
NICE TO SEE YOU AGAIN.

26:01.660 --> 26:04.128
OH.

26:04.130 --> 26:06.155
LOVELY.

26:13.400 --> 26:14.435
HI.

26:15.170 --> 26:20.039
ANY IDEA HOW THIS GUM GOT
FROM YOUR MOUTH TO THAT CHAIR?

26:21.210 --> 26:23.770
I THOUGHT THIS WAS SUPPOSED
TO BE A GOOD SCHOOL.

26:23.780 --> 26:27.204
SHOULDN'T YOU BE,
LIKE, SMART?

26:37.930 --> 26:39.283
Cliff: SO,
SPEAKING OF DOWN AND DIRTY,

26:39.290 --> 26:41.190
YOU WOULDN'T BELIEVE
THE DIVORCE CASE I'VE GOT.

26:41.200 --> 26:44.124
LADY STOLE
FROM HER HUSBAND REPEATEDLY,

26:44.130 --> 26:47.861
STOLE FROM HIS CHILDREN,
HAD HIS DOG PUT TO SLEEP.

26:47.870 --> 26:49.292
AND LET THE RECORD SHOW

26:49.300 --> 26:51.109
THE DOG WAS QUITE SURPRISED
BY THIS DECISION.

26:51.110 --> 26:53.931
THE WOMAN SLEPT
WITH . . . EVERYONE.

26:53.940 --> 26:58.172
AND LET ME GUESS --
SHE'S YOUR CLIENT.

26:58.180 --> 26:59.602
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:59.610 --> 27:01.168
[ DOOR OPENS ]

27:01.180 --> 27:03.273
GENTLEM EN.

27:03.280 --> 27:04.747
IS THIS THE ONE?

27:04.750 --> 27:06.149
NO, THERE'S YOUR GUY.

27:06.150 --> 27:08.357
CAN I HELP YOU FELLAS
WITH SOMETHING?

27:08.360 --> 27:10.988
THIS IS DETECTIVE SANCHEZ
WITH THE LAPD.

27:10.990 --> 27:14.118
SIR, IS THIS YOUR CARD?

27:14.130 --> 27:16.098
YEAH.

27:16.100 --> 27:17.920
YOU PRESENTED YOURSELF
AS AN ADRIAN MONK,

27:17.930 --> 27:20.228
LOS ANGELES COUNTY
BUILDING INSPECTOR?

27:20.230 --> 27:22.630
AND I BELIEVE THAT'S YOUR
CELLPHONE NUMBER WRITTEN ON IT?

27:22.640 --> 27:24.198
AND?

27:24.210 --> 27:26.064
THE APARTMENT COMPLEX MANAGER
THAT YOU HANDED THAT TO

27:26.070 --> 27:28.538
SAYS YOU ORDERED HIM
TO LET YOU INTO THE APARTMENT

27:28.540 --> 27:29.700
OF STEVEN BATANDO.

27:29.710 --> 27:31.598
ORDERED?
ASKED POLITELY MAYBE.

27:31.610 --> 27:33.168
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:36.920 --> 27:39.013
CONGRATULATIONS, BOYS.
YOU GOT ME.

27:39.020 --> 27:40.544
THAT'S A GOOD ONE,
MR. MARS.

27:40.550 --> 27:43.018
BUT I'M AFRAID THAT
IMPERSONATING A COUNTY EMPLOYEE

27:43.020 --> 27:44.385
IS THE LEAST
OF YOUR PROBLEMS.

27:44.390 --> 27:46.858
BATANDO'S BEEN MISSING
FOR 52 HOURS.

27:46.860 --> 27:48.396
GUESS WHAT, KEITH --

27:48.400 --> 27:50.823
YOU'RE THE LEADING SUSPECT
IN HIS DISAPPEARANCE.

28:04.710 --> 28:07.440
SO, MR. MARS,
YOU MIND TELLING US

28:07.450 --> 28:09.315
WHAT YOU WERE LOOKING FOR
IN MR. BATANDO'S APARTMENT?

28:09.320 --> 28:11.140
Lamb: THE MAN'S GIRLFRIEND
WAS WORRIED SICK.

28:11.150 --> 28:13.516
YOU SHOULD HAVE SEEN HER CRYING,
KEITH.

28:13.520 --> 28:15.056
IT WAS HEARTBREAKING.

28:15.060 --> 28:17.358
EXCUSE ME, OFFICERS,
BUT IF I DON'T BRING UP THE LAW,

28:17.360 --> 28:20.022
THEN THIS WON'T BE CONSIDERED
A BILLABLE HOUR.

28:20.030 --> 28:22.328
DO YOU PLAN
ON CHARGING MY CLIENT?

28:23.430 --> 28:24.988
GREAT.

28:25.000 --> 28:26.820
IF YOU'D LIKE TO TALK WITH HIM
FURTHER, CALL MY OFFICE.

28:26.830 --> 28:28.366
I'LL SET AN APPOINTMENT.

28:28.370 --> 28:29.359
MY CARD.

28:29.370 --> 28:30.496
I KNOW YOUR NUMBER.

28:30.500 --> 28:32.161
IT'S ALL OVER THE BUS BENCHES.

28:32.170 --> 28:33.831
"CALL CLIFF AND GET OFF."

28:33.840 --> 28:35.068
PLUS, IT'S A RADIO JINGLE.

28:35.080 --> 28:36.707
* CALL 555 -- *

28:36.710 --> 28:39.838
WELL, YOU KNOW THE REST.

28:41.080 --> 28:43.310
WE'LL BE KEEPING AN EYE ON YOU,
MR. MARS.

28:47.620 --> 28:50.009
[ SIGHS ]

28:50.020 --> 28:52.250
NICE WORK, CLIFF.

28:53.290 --> 28:55.997
WHEN YOU'RE HERE,
YOU'RE FAMILY.

28:56.000 --> 28:58.719
OKAY, THANK YOU.

28:58.730 --> 29:00.197
[ RECEIVER THUDS ]

29:00.200 --> 29:02.464
JASON O'DELL
WAS DISCHARGED YESTERDAY.

29:02.470 --> 29:05.007
YOU THINK THE DEAN AND HIS WIFE
KIDNAPPED BATANDO?

29:05.010 --> 29:06.864
IT LOOKS THAT WAY.

29:06.870 --> 29:08.599
THEY ASKED HIM
FOR HIS BONE MARROW.

29:08.610 --> 29:09.872
BATAN DO SAID NO.

29:09.880 --> 29:11.745
THESE THINGS
TEND TO END BADLY, KEITH.

29:11.750 --> 29:15.470
THERE'S NOT MUCH MOTIVATION TO
KEEP THE UNWILLING DONOR ALIVE.

29:15.480 --> 29:18.278
THEY TEND TO EXPIRE
ON THE OPERATING TABLE.

29:18.290 --> 29:21.214
IT'S TOUGH TO PRESS CHARGES
WHEN YOU'RE SIX FEET UNDER.

29:21.220 --> 29:22.983
I'M GONNA TRACK DOWN
THE O'DELLS,

29:22.990 --> 29:24.958
SCARE THE DEAN
IF I CAN FIND HIM.

29:24.960 --> 29:26.655
I'M GONNA NEED SOME HELP.

29:26.660 --> 29:28.992
YOU STILL GOT YOUR RESEARCHER
WORKINYEEPOR YOU?

29:29.000 --> 29:30.991
WHATEVER YOU NEED.

29:32.330 --> 29:35.436
OH, YOU STILL IN TOWN?
YOU HAVEN'T SKIPPED YET?

29:35.440 --> 29:37.431
WHERE'S YOUR WIFE'S
EX-HUSBAND?

29:37.440 --> 29:39.237
WHERE'S YOUR STEPSON?

29:39.240 --> 29:40.309
MEXICO.

29:40.310 --> 29:43.108
JUST GOT OFF THE PHONE
WITH MY WIFE.

29:43.110 --> 29:44.407
SHE TOOK JASON TO ROSARITO.

29:44.410 --> 29:46.173
SHE WON'T TELL ME
WHICH HOSPITAL,

29:46.180 --> 29:47.442
BUT THEY'RE MOVING FORWARD.

29:47.450 --> 29:49.247
MINDY'S BROTHER
IS HELPING HER.

29:49.250 --> 29:52.185
I'M GONNA LOSE THEM BOTH,
KEITH -- MY STEPSON, MY WIFE --

29:52.190 --> 29:54.784
ALL BECAUSE OF THAT
SELFISH SON OF A BITCH.

29:54.790 --> 29:56.417
I'LL TRACK THEM DOWN.

29:56.420 --> 29:58.183
I'M GOING WITH YOU.

29:58.190 --> 30:00.624
YOU'RE GONNA NEED
TO TRACE HER CALL, RIGHT?

30:00.630 --> 30:02.029
PROBABLY, YEAH.

30:02.030 --> 30:03.998
HOW DO YOU PLAN
ON KEEPING HER ON THE LINE?

30:04.000 --> 30:05.365
I CAN SAY HALF A SENTENCE

30:05.370 --> 30:07.565
AND GET HER TO YELL AT ME
FOR THREE HOURS.

30:13.740 --> 30:15.276
YOU RANG?

30:15.280 --> 30:16.929
IF THERE
WAS ANYBODY ELSE...

30:16.940 --> 30:19.704
ONE OF THE OTHER
MAINTENANCE GUYS FOUND THE MASKS

30:19.710 --> 30:22.474
USED IN THE HOLDUP IN A DUMPSTER
BEHIND BENNIS HALL.

30:22.480 --> 30:23.708
HE FOUND THE GUNS, TOO.

30:23.720 --> 30:25.187
HE CAME TO ME
INSTEAD OF GOING TO LAMB

30:25.190 --> 30:27.750
'CAUSE HE WASN'T SURE
IF IT'D HURT ME OR HELP ME.

30:27.750 --> 30:29.183
I'M NOT REALLY SURE EITHER.

30:29.190 --> 30:30.817
I CAN TRACK THE OWNERSHIP
HISTORY OF THE GUNS

30:30.820 --> 30:32.082
TO SEE WHERE IT LEADS.

30:32.090 --> 30:35.526
YEAH, UH,
I DOUBT THAT'S GONNA WORK.

30:36.700 --> 30:38.361
THE GUNS AREN'T REAL.

30:38.370 --> 30:39.860
THEY'RE FAKES.

30:49.340 --> 30:50.671
UH, EXCUSE ME?

30:50.680 --> 30:52.079
YEAH.

30:52.080 --> 30:54.116
CAN SOMEONE POINT ME
TO THE PROPS DEPARTMENT?

30:54.120 --> 30:55.519
JENNY'S PROPS.

30:55.520 --> 30:56.714
WHERE COULD I FIND --

30:56.720 --> 30:58.779
I'M JENNY.
WHAT DO YOU NEED?

30:58.790 --> 31:00.109
UM...

31:00.120 --> 31:02.259
SOMEONE HELD UP
AN ON-CAMPUS CASINO

31:02.260 --> 31:03.784
USING A COUPLE OF PROP GUNS.

31:03.790 --> 31:06.987
WE'RE THE THEATER DEPARTMENT.
WE DON'T DO GUNS.

31:06.990 --> 31:08.196
WE DO MOLIRE.

31:08.200 --> 31:10.225
YOU WANT
A POOR MAN'S TARANTINO,

31:10.230 --> 31:12.767
THAT WOULD BE
THE FILM DEPARTMENT.

31:12.770 --> 31:14.362
IF YOU SEE THEM,

31:14.370 --> 31:16.861
TELL THEM WE JUST LOVED THEIR
LITTLE OPENING-NIGHT PRESENT.

31:16.870 --> 31:18.064
WHICH IS?

31:18.070 --> 31:20.607
OUR STAGE
IS COVERED IN PAM.

31:20.610 --> 31:21.872
WHO'S PAM?

31:21.880 --> 31:23.370
PAM IS A COOKING SPRAY.

31:23.380 --> 31:25.644
WE CAN'T WALK OUT THERE
WITHOUT FALLING ON OUR ASSES.

31:25.650 --> 31:28.642
WE HAD THE TEMERITY
TO SCHEDULE OUR OPENING NIGHT

31:28.650 --> 31:31.619
ON THE SAME WEEKEND
AS THEIR SHORT-FILM FESTIVAL.

31:31.620 --> 31:34.953
MAYBE THIS IS THEIR WAY
OF SAYING, "BREAK A LEG."

31:37.790 --> 31:39.121
THANK YOU! GOOD NIGHT!

31:39.130 --> 31:40.825
HERE ALL WEEK.
TRY THE VEAL.

31:40.830 --> 31:42.991
AND SCENE.

31:44.100 --> 31:46.967
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

31:53.840 --> 31:55.569
YEAH?

31:55.580 --> 31:57.730
ONE OF THE GUYS ON THE TEAM
SAID I SHOULD --
UH-HUH.

31:57.740 --> 31:59.173
INSTRUCTOR AND CLASS.

31:59.180 --> 32:00.977
WINKLER. ENGINEERING.

32:00.980 --> 32:03.574
COME IN. CLOSE THE DOOR.

32:06.520 --> 32:10.354
WINKLER'S USED THE SAME EXAMS
FOR THE PAST THREE YEARS.

32:13.090 --> 32:16.628
THIS FILE
DOES NOT CONTAIN THE EXAMS.

32:16.630 --> 32:17.927
IT'S A STUDY GUIDE.

32:17.930 --> 32:19.966
IF YOU WANT THE STUDY GUIDE,
IT'S $100.

32:19.970 --> 32:23.133
IF YOU WANT THE ANSWERS TO THE
STUDY GUIDE, IT'S ANOTHER $100.

32:23.140 --> 32:25.108
IT'S A STUDY GUIDE, HUH?

32:25.110 --> 32:27.908
YEAH,
IT'S $200 FOR THE SET.

32:27.910 --> 32:31.073
I'LL TAKE THE GUIDE.

32:31.080 --> 32:34.345
YOU KEEP THE ANSWERS.

32:39.920 --> 32:42.559
[ SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYS ]

32:44.830 --> 32:46.422
FIND US SEATS.

32:46.430 --> 32:49.649
I'M GONNA GET US SOME POPCORN
AND GRILL ME SOME FILM GEEKS.

32:49.660 --> 32:50.729
UH, VERONICA?

32:50.730 --> 32:52.163
YEAH?

32:52.170 --> 32:55.560
YOU KNOW THAT WHOLE
"LIFE IMITATES ART" THING?

32:55.570 --> 32:57.333
YOU READY TO SCREW 'EM,
DICK?

32:57.340 --> 32:58.705
YEAH, COVER ME, JIMMY.

32:58.710 --> 33:00.735
ALL RIGHT,
HANDS IN THE AIR, BUDDY.

33:00.740 --> 33:01.832
STICK 'EM UP.

33:01.840 --> 33:03.137
GIVE ME THE MONEY.

33:03.140 --> 33:05.449
RIGHT NOW, YOU SEE.
RIGHT NOW.

33:05.450 --> 33:07.577
AND DON'T FORGET TO VOTE.

33:12.590 --> 33:15.058
LOVED YOUR MOVIE.
8 MILLIMETER -- BOLD CHOICE.

33:15.060 --> 33:16.584
YEAH.

33:16.590 --> 33:18.626
SO, IN OTHER NEWS,
AN ARMED ROBBERY WAS COMMITTED

33:18.630 --> 33:20.780
WITH THE MASKS AND GUNS
USED IN YOUR LITTLE FILM.

33:20.790 --> 33:23.429
I WAS HOPING YOU COULD TELL ME
WHERE I MIGHT FIND THOSE.

33:23.430 --> 33:25.295
YOU'RE LOGAN ECHOLLS,
RIGHT?

33:25.300 --> 33:27.165
I HEARD
YOU WERE GOING HERE.

33:27.170 --> 33:28.865
DID YOU EVER THINK
OF INVESTING IN --

33:28.870 --> 33:29.859
NO.

33:29.870 --> 33:32.065
HEY, BUDDY, RIGHT HERE.

33:32.070 --> 33:34.004
YOU CAN SCHMOOZE LATER.

33:34.010 --> 33:35.671
THE GUNS AND THE MASKS
WERE STOLEN.

33:35.680 --> 33:38.069
OUR WHOLE EQUIPMENT TRUCK
DISAPPEARED A WEEK AGO.

33:38.080 --> 33:39.502
DID YOU REPORT IT?

33:39.510 --> 33:41.546
YEAH, THE CAMPUS POLICE
ACTUALLY TRACKED IT DOWN.

33:41.550 --> 33:43.541
CAN YOU BELIEVE IT?
RENT-A-COPS.

33:43.550 --> 33:45.541
WE GOT
ALL OUR EQUIPMENT BACK.

33:45.550 --> 33:48.110
ONLY THING MISSING
WERE THE GUNS AND THE MASKS.

34:10.310 --> 34:12.346
Woman on P.A.:
DR. GARCIA, POR FAVOR...

34:12.350 --> 34:13.908
CALL HER AGAIN.

34:13.910 --> 34:15.172
IT'S NOT GONNA WORK.

34:15.180 --> 34:17.910
MINDY'S NOT GONNA PICK UP
THE PHONE.

34:17.920 --> 34:19.387
AND I'M NO EXPERT,

34:19.390 --> 34:20.880
BUT I'M PRETTY SURE
YOU CAN'T TRACE A PHONE CALL

34:20.890 --> 34:23.654
IF THE PERSON ON THE OTHER END
WON'T PICK UP THE PHONE.

34:23.660 --> 34:25.082
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

34:25.090 --> 34:26.785
DR. RODRIGUEZ, POR FAVOR...

34:26.790 --> 34:28.428
CLIFF?

34:34.800 --> 34:36.859
THANKS, CLIFF.

34:38.070 --> 34:41.130
YOU'VE GOT HIM AT
SISTERS OF MERCY IN SAN DIEGO.

34:41.140 --> 34:42.937
MINDY'S UNCLE'S
AN ONCOLOGIST THERE.

34:42.940 --> 34:46.546
DO YOU EXPECT ME TO APOLOGIZE,
KEITH? HE'S MY SON.

34:46.550 --> 34:50.213
HOW'D YOU GET BATANDO ADMITTED?
YOU BRING HIM IN UNCONSCIOUS?

34:50.220 --> 34:52.313
WHAT CHOICE
DID HE LEAVE US?

35:38.600 --> 35:40.124
WHO ARE YOU?

35:40.130 --> 35:41.791
COME ON, YOU REMEMBER ME.

35:41.800 --> 35:43.631
I'M THE GIRL
WHOSE NECKLACE YOU STOLE.

35:43.640 --> 35:46.859
IT'S GOT SENTIMENTAL VALUE.
I WANT IT BACK.

35:46.870 --> 35:48.235
I SEE.

35:48.240 --> 35:50.208
I'LL TAKE TWO BOXES
OF THE THIN MINTS

35:50.210 --> 35:51.768
AND SOME LEMON COOLERS.

35:51.780 --> 35:54.647
YOU CAN KEEP ALL THE GAMBLING
MONEY, EVERYTHING ELSE.

35:54.650 --> 35:55.969
I DON'T CARE.

35:55.980 --> 35:58.119
JUST GIVE ME MY NECKLACE BACK,
AND WE'LL BE COOL.

35:58.120 --> 36:00.987
WOW, THAT'S SOME
HARDCORE SALESMANSHIP.

36:00.990 --> 36:02.958
YOU'RE GOOD.

36:02.960 --> 36:05.758
TELL YOU WHAT -- THROW IN A BOX
OF THE SHORTBREAD.

36:05.760 --> 36:07.557
YOU AND YOUR PARTNER
ROBBED THE CASINO.

36:07.560 --> 36:10.199
YOU DID ALL THE TALKING
BECAUSE OF SASAKI'S ACCENT.

36:10.200 --> 36:12.225
AS SECURITY OFFICERS,

36:12.230 --> 36:15.233
THE CRIMINAL RECORDS OF ALL
NEW EMPLOYEES CROSS YOUR DESK.

36:15.240 --> 36:18.562
YOU DECIDE TO PIN YOUR CRIME ON
THE NEW EX-CON MAINTENANCE GUY

36:18.570 --> 36:20.765
YOU SEE EVERY DAY
JUST OUTSIDE YOUR OFFICE.

36:20.770 --> 36:24.240
THIS ALSO EXPLAINS WHY YOU
WERE COVERED IN DRYWALL DUST.

36:24.250 --> 36:25.740
YOU KNEW ABOUT THE CASINO.

36:25.750 --> 36:27.741
YOU EVEN TRIED TO SHUT IT DOWN
A COUPLE TIMES,

36:27.750 --> 36:30.571
BUT THOSE SPOILED COLLEGE BOYS
DIDN'T LISTEN TO YOU.

36:30.580 --> 36:33.879
I'M GUESSING YOU GOT THE IDEA
WHEN YOU FOUND THE MASKS

36:33.890 --> 36:36.450
AND PROP GUNS
IN THE FILM-DEPARTMENT VAN.

36:36.460 --> 36:39.156
[ Hispanic accent]
YOU THINK I MISSED ANYTHING?

36:39.160 --> 36:42.220
WELL, ONE THING -- PROOF.

36:42.230 --> 36:43.822
[ Normal voice ]
NOT QUITE TRUE.

36:45.930 --> 36:47.363
LOOK WHAT I HAVE.

36:47.370 --> 36:48.792
WHAT? PRINTS?

36:48.800 --> 36:51.360
THE WITNESSES SAID
THE HOLDUP MEN WORE GLOVES.

36:51.370 --> 36:53.964
YEAH, BUT YOU WOULDN'T BELIEVE
HOW MUCH HAIR

36:53.970 --> 36:55.198
IS INSIDE THESE MASKS.

36:55.210 --> 36:57.474
IT'S KIND OF GROSS,
ACTUALLY.

36:57.480 --> 36:59.004
IT'S LIKE A SACK OF DNA.

36:59.010 --> 37:02.309
SO, I'LL TRADE YOU --
THIS BAG FOR MY NECKLACE.

37:05.050 --> 37:06.586
[ GROWLING ]

37:10.290 --> 37:13.225
I'LL NEED A DAY
TO GET YOUR NECKLACE BACK.

37:13.230 --> 37:16.427
YEAH,
THAT'S NOT GONNA DO IT.

37:16.430 --> 37:18.864
[ SIREN WAILS ]

37:18.870 --> 37:20.724
WHAT DID YOU DO?

37:22.140 --> 37:26.668
[ Imitating Tony Montana ]
SAY HELLO TO MY LI'I'I'LE FRIEND.

37:32.510 --> 37:34.273
KEITH, PLEASE,
I'M BEGGING YOU.

37:34.280 --> 37:36.271
KEITH, FOR GOD'S SAKE,
JUST HEAR ME OUT.

37:36.280 --> 37:38.248
I'VE BEEN HEARING YOU OUT
SINCE MEXICO.

37:38.250 --> 37:40.115
I'M DONE, CYRUS.
THIS GAME IS OVER.

37:40.120 --> 37:41.610
IT'S NOT A GAME.

37:41.620 --> 37:43.850
YOU NEED ME TO GET ON MY KNEES,
I'LL GET ON MY KNEES.

37:43.860 --> 37:45.782
YOU STOP THAT OPERATION,
THAT'S IT.

37:45.790 --> 37:47.223
MY SON'S DEAD.
HE'S 9 YEARS OLD.

37:47.230 --> 37:49.152
YOU GO UP THERE, HE DIES.

37:49.160 --> 37:51.799
IF I STAY DOWN HERE,
I'M PARTLY RESPONSIBLE
FOR ANOTHER DEAD MAN.

37:51.800 --> 37:54.291
THE ONLY WAY YOU AND YOUR WIFE
GET AWAY WITH THIS

37:54.300 --> 37:56.530
IS IF BATANDO DIES.

37:56.540 --> 37:58.804
WE'RE NOT GONNA LET
BATANDO DIE.

37:58.810 --> 38:00.698
THAT'S NOT THE PLAN,
I SWEAR.

38:00.710 --> 38:03.304
THEN YOU, YOUR WIFE, AND YOUR
WIFE'S FAMILY MEMBERS WHO HELPED

38:03.310 --> 38:05.141
ARE GOING TO PRISON
FOR A VERY LONG TIME.

38:05.150 --> 38:06.572
AND JASON WILL LIVE.

38:06.580 --> 38:09.811
SMALL PRICE TO PAY,
DON'T YOU THINK?

38:09.820 --> 38:12.641
WHAT WOULD YOU DO
IF IT WERE VERONICA?

38:18.260 --> 38:20.125
FIND MY NECKLACE?

38:20.130 --> 38:21.279
NOPE.

38:21.290 --> 38:23.292
BUT WE FOUND
A DOZEN OTHER ITEMS --

38:23.300 --> 38:26.189
COUPLE ROLEXES,
DOZENS OF CREDIT CARDS.

38:26.200 --> 38:27.565
THESE ARE THE GUYS.

38:27.570 --> 38:29.367
MAYBE THE OTHER ONE
HAS YOUR NECKLACE.

38:29.370 --> 38:31.759
WE HAVE A CAR ON THE WAY
OVER THERE RIGHT NOW.

38:31.770 --> 38:33.635
OH, LOOK.

38:33.640 --> 38:36.234
SOMEONE TIPPED OFF
THE LOCAL NEWS.

38:36.240 --> 38:37.468
THAT'S MY CUE.

38:37.480 --> 38:39.573
DO YOU SEE
HOW WELL THIS WORKS

38:39.580 --> 38:42.344
WHEN YOU PLAY BY THE RULES,
VERONICA?

38:42.350 --> 38:45.387
[ JOHNNY CASH'S "BUSTED" PLAYS ]

38:50.620 --> 38:52.952
* MY BILLS ARE ALL DUE *

38:52.960 --> 38:55.292
* AND THE BABIES NEED SHOES *

38:55.300 --> 38:57.757
* BUT I'M BUSTED *

38:59.230 --> 39:02.097
* COTTON IS DOWN *

39:02.100 --> 39:04.261
* TO A QUARTER A POUND *

39:04.270 --> 39:06.465
* AND I'M BUSTED *

39:08.440 --> 39:10.908
* I GOT A COW THAT WENT DRY *

39:10.910 --> 39:13.242
* AND A HEN THAT WON'T LAY *

39:13.250 --> 39:14.842
* A BIG STACK OF BILLS... *

39:14.850 --> 39:16.977
YOU THINK YOU'RE SUCH
A BIG DEAL, BUT YOU'RE SO NOT.

39:16.980 --> 39:19.380
YOU DID THIS. YOU SET UP
MY DADDY, YOU STUPID COW.

39:19.390 --> 39:21.039
GO BACK TO HEARST
WHERE YOU BELONG.

39:21.050 --> 39:24.486
YOU COME INTO THIS TOWN
AND TREAT EVERYONE LIKE DIRT.

39:31.360 --> 39:33.089
* I WENT TO MY BROTHER *

39:33.100 --> 39:35.967
* TO ASK FOR A LOAN *

39:35.970 --> 39:38.097
* I WAS BUSTED *

39:38.970 --> 39:41.837
* I HATE TO BEG *

39:41.840 --> 39:44.206
* LIKE A DOG FOR A BONE *

39:44.210 --> 39:45.746
* BUT I'M BUSTED *

39:48.750 --> 39:50.149
* MY BROTHER SAID *

39:50.150 --> 39:53.381
* "THERE AIN'T A THING
I CAN DO *

39:53.390 --> 39:55.517
* "MY WIFE AND MY KIDS *

39:55.520 --> 39:58.785
* ARE ALL DOWN WITH THE FLU" *

39:59.890 --> 40:01.357
Keith: DON?

40:01.360 --> 40:05.364
MEET STEVE BATANDO. I BELIEVE
YOU WERE LOOKING FOR HIM.

40:05.370 --> 40:06.826
YOU'RE STEVEN BATAN DO?

40:06.830 --> 40:10.266
AND I WANT TO APOLOGIZE
FOR CAUSING SO MUCH TROUBLE.

40:10.270 --> 40:12.704
I MEAN, I HAD NO IDEA
PEOPLE WERE LOOKING FOR ME.

40:12.710 --> 40:17.272
I JUST WENT CAMPING FOR A WEEK
AND DIDN'T TELL ANYBODY,

40:17.280 --> 40:18.679
LEFT MY CELLPHONE.

40:18.680 --> 40:21.444
I MEAN, I CAN'T BELIEVE
I CAUSED ALL THIS FUSS.

40:21.450 --> 40:25.489
IT WOULD BE FUNNY IF IT WASN'T
SO ALMOST, I MEAN, YOU KNOW --

40:25.490 --> 40:27.742
RIDICULOUS?

40:27.750 --> 40:29.479
YEAH.

40:34.560 --> 40:37.199
YOU TELL MY EX-WIFE
I OWN HER NOW.

40:37.200 --> 40:41.193
NO MORE TALK OF ALIMONY,
NO MORE CHILD SUPPORT.

40:41.200 --> 40:43.259
WE'RE BEYOND EVEN.

40:43.270 --> 40:47.161
IT'S BEEN MADE VERY CLEAR
IN THE DOCUMENTS YOU SIGNED.

40:47.170 --> 40:48.671
NICE RIDE, HUH?

40:48.680 --> 40:50.875
THINK OF IT
AS A FATHER'S DAY GIFT.

40:53.250 --> 40:56.139
[ SIGHS ]

40:56.150 --> 40:59.745
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

41:22.580 --> 41:26.402
WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
THIS IS THE GUY?

41:26.410 --> 41:27.968
THE FIFTH VICTIM, CLAIRE,

41:27.980 --> 41:30.540
WAS CAUGHT IN AN ATM PHOTO
